<TITLE>The time is right for Red Wings to be sellers at trade deadline</TITLE>
<TEXT>
By Published 4:59 p.m. MT Jan. 27, 2017 | Updated 5:15 p.m. MT Jan. 27, 2017 
    
Drew Miller, left, and Tomas Jurco of the Detroit Red Wings celebrate a goal against the New York Islanders on March 29, 2015, in Uniondale, New York. (Photo: Bruce Bennett, ) 
  
